This product includes software developed by Folarin Shonibare
(https://github.com/omofolarin/strategic-thinking).

The architectural design of this project draws on:
  - Dixit, A. K., & Nalebuff, B. J. (1991). Thinking Strategically:
    The Competitive Edge in Business, Politics, and Everyday Life.
  - Schelling, T. C. (1960). The Strategy of Conflict.

These works are not included in, nor required by, the distribution;
they are cited in provenance metadata to ground strategic explanations
in their theoretical origins.
